SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT STCY_CURRENCY, STCY_TOTADEBTNOTESMENTIONED, STCY_TOTACREDNOTESMENTIONED
FROM :1, :2
WHERE SCHT_ADMNO = :3 AND SCHT_CLNTNO =:4 AND SCHT_BOOKED <> 'Y' AND STCY_SCHT_NO = SCHT_NO
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

SELECT CAST( SUM(BTCP_AMOUNTCURRH) AS DECIMAL(13,2)) FROM :1/BTCP, :1/BTCH WHERE BTCP_ADMNO_INITIAL = :2 AND BTCP_CLNTNO_INITIAL = :3 AND BTCP_STATUS <2 and BTCP_BTCH_ID = BTCH_ID and BTCP_LASTLINEBTPC = 0 and (BTCH_CODETYPEACCOUNT is null or BTCH_CODETYPEACCOUNT <> 5)

Select cast(sum(CDEP_ACTUALAMOUNTCLNT) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CDEP_ACTUALAMOUNTHELL) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/CDEP where CDEP_ADMNO = :2 and CDEP_CLNTNO = :3 and CDEP_TYPE = 4 for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
